        <t:abstract>
        <t:p>A kind of extended monastic history of Ethiopia in the version of
          <t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0341DL">the monastery Dabra Libānos</t:placeName>
          developed from the monastic genealogy of <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9162TaklaHa">St Takla Hāymānot</t:persName>,
          that shows his spiritual descendance from <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1962Anthony">St Anthony</t:persName>. Partly
           based on <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3973GadlaT">the Vita of Takla Hāymānot</t:ref>.
         </t:p>
        </t:abstract>
