         <t:div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
           <t:note>The text below follows the edition <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/CB9GUS9K"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Getachew1983monastic"/><title level="a">The Monastic Genealogy of the Line of Täklä Haymanot of Shoa</title><title level="j">Rassegna di Studi Etiopici</title><author><name>Getatchew Haile</name></author><date>1982_1983</date><biblScope unit="volume">29</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">7-38</biblScope><note type="url">http://www.jstor.org/stable/41299670</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Täklä Haymanot</note><note type="tag">bm:Getachew1983monastic</note><note type="tag">bm:Getatchew1982Monast</note></note><note type="tag">Täklä Haymanot</note><note type="tag">bm:Getachew1983monastic</note><note type="tag">bm:Getatchew1982Monast</note></t:bibl>.
         </t:note>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                <t:ab>
                  ንጽሕፍ፡ እንከ፡ ልደተ፡ አበዊነ፡ መነኮሳት። አባ፡ እንጦንስ፡ ለብሰ፡ ልብሰ፡ ምንኵስና፡ በእደ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡
                  አባ፡ እንጦንስ፡ ወለዶ፡ ለአባ፡ መቃርስ፡ ዘየዓቢ። ወአባ፡ መቃርስ፡ ወለዶ፡ ለአባ፡ ጳኵሚስ፡ አበ፡ ማኅበር።
                  ወአባ፡ ጳኵሚስ፡ ወለዶ፡ ለአባ፡ ቴዎድሮስ።
                  ወአባ፡ ቴዎድሮስ፡ ወለዶ፡ ለአባ፡ አረጋዊ፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ዘሚካኤል።
                </t:ab>

             </t:div>

            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                <t:ab>
                  ወለእለ፡ ተርፉ፡ ካልዓን፡ ንቡራነ፡ እድ፡ እለ፡ ጽሑፋን፡ ውስተ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ዜና፡ ሀሎ፡ ጽሑፍ፡ ወሰኖሙ፡ በበበሐውርቲሆሙ።
                  እግዚአብሔር፡ ይዕቀበነ፡ በጸሎቶሙ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።
                </t:ab>
             </t:div>
